                                <path d="M10 9V0h12v9H10zm12 5h10v18H0V14h10v9h12v-9z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
        <span style="display:inline-block;padding:2px 3px">Tomasz Sroka</span>
    </a>
</div>
